FT  22 JUL 92 / UK Company News: GWR loss nearly doubled to Dollars 13.6m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Great Western Resources, the US-based oil, gas and coal company which has a
USM quote, fell deeper into the red in the half year to March 31 with a
pre-tax loss of Dollars 13.6m (Pounds 7.1m) against Dollars 7.3m.
Losses per share were 15 cents (8 cents) and there is no interim dividend
(2.5p gross).
