<TEXT>
SOUTHWEST Airlines, the low-cost Dallas-based carrier which specialises in
flying heavily travelled commuter routes, yesterday showed up its larger
rivals when it reported a Dollars 23.5m profit after tax in the three months
to end-June, writes Nikki Tait.
