construction group where he spent six years.
He replaces William McGrath who became acting managing director of Norwest
Holst following the departure of Chris Bucknall who, after only a few months
in the job, returned to Compass Services, the contract catering and health
services company, where he became managing director.
Peter Mason, formerly executive chairman of Norwest Holst, earlier this year
replaced David Cawthra as chief executive of Balfour Beatty, the
construction arm of BICC engineering group, when he moved to the Miller
Group.
